    <item>
      <title>美国股票反弹，因为贸易商在特朗普关税之前覆盖短裤</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/us-stocks-slide-as-economic-worries-flare-ahead-of-trump-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统在闭幕式之后，唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）在总统的关税宣布之前，美国股票反弹，而边缘交易者缩短了赌注，并堆放在一些受到殴打的市场上的最危险的角落。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/us-stocks-slide-as-economic-worries-flare-ahead-of-trump-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 13:50:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Grifols家族确认与Brookfield的接管有关</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/brookfield-is-said-to-revive-talks-on-potential-grifols-offer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[与家族有联系的四个投资集团拥有约35％的Grifols SA，证实他们正在与Brookfield Asset Management Ltd.进行谈判。去年尝试失败后，西班牙血液流质公司的潜在报价。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/brookfield-is-said-to-revive-talks-on-potential-grifols-offer</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 08:22:13 GMT</pubDate>
